Benjamin Michael Lee (born 11 September 1978 in Sydney, Australia) is an ARIA
Award winning Australian indie pop musician and actor. Lee began his career as a
musician at the age of 14 with the Sydney band Noise Addict, but focused on his
solo career when the band broke up.


The Rebirth of Venus is the seventh studio album by Australian indie pop
musician Ben Lee. Ben describes the new album as "uplifting, joyful, beautifully
chaotic, opinionated, confused, passionate and real" and an entirely different
beast from the classic pop album, Ripe.
